Reviewed actual implementation in commit f4d43538 (referenced as `result_rev` in the result.json). The diff in the review only shows the execution metadata; the implementation is in `crates/axon-cypher/src/memory_store.rs` and `lib.rs`.

AC1: `QueryStore` trait defined at memory_store.rs:19. AC2: `MemoryQueryStore` with `insert_entity`/`insert_link` for hand-built entities and typed links with `PropertyMap`. AC3: `EntityStream`/`LinkStream` boxed iterators (streaming), `EntityScan` (label + property filters), `LinkTraversal` (anchor + Direction + types + filters), `get_entity`/`get_link` by id; no `axon-storage` import. AC4: Four focused tests (entity scan, lookup, outgoing typed traversal, incoming/Either with directed indexes).

Notable: `Direction` is reused from `crate::ast`, which is appropriate. Link IDs auto-derive as `source/type/target`, with a `with_id` escape hatch. Direction::Either dedupes via `BTreeSet`.

